item.title: #320 Back Pain Myths, Facts & Everyday Fixes with Consultant Spinal Neurosurgeon Mr Anthony Ghosh
item.description: Back pain is one of the most common health issues worldwide yet it’s still surrounded by confusion, fear, and myths. In this episode, I sit down with Anthony Ghosh, Consultant Spinal Neurosurgeon, educator and founder of Spine MDT Clinic to separate fact from fiction and give you a practical toolkit for a healthier spine...
